/-!
###############################################################################
# Autonomy Valuation
###############################################################################

This file introduces the abstract notion of a derived valuation
specific to autonomy.

Autonomy valuation evaluates effective freedom from constraint
under structural, contextual, and agreement-mediated conditions.

Autonomy valuation does NOT:
• define autonomy
• assert moral worth
• justify authority
• mandate protection
-Imply Consent
-Imply legitimacy or authority
-Justify Intervention or coercion

It is a descriptive valuation only.
###############################################################################
-/

namespace SigmaR

/--
An autonomy-specific derived valuation.
-/
constant AutonomyValuation : Type

end SigmaR
